  "description": "面向 [Polymarket](https://polymarket.com) 的量化交易基础设施，包含市场深度筛选器与中文开发文档知识库。",
  "main": "index.js",
  "scripts": {
    "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1",
    "compile": "hardhat compile",
